{"tid":949945,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"話說做冬唔凍農曆新年就會勁凍","createTime":"2018-12-21T07:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T08:44:28.000Z","uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1573fe656a3b2f745232ff97d293f777e6aea79","tid":949945,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"今年過年會唔會又係得幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b047f89ad6f43a5a86b8b25c3da176d89faadbc","tid":949945,"uid":103617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1573fe656a3b2f745232ff97d293f777e6aea79","tid":949945,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"今年過年會唔會又係得幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422f1f2e377c64b3f02fc90daad39fcae416a663","tid":949945,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b047f89ad6f43a5a86b8b25c3da176d89faadbc","tid":949945,"uid":103617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1573fe656a3b2f745232ff97d293f777e6aea79","tid":949945,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"今年過年會唔會又係得幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5ffdf3798c332923dd9ff4d579aa707e19a2a0","tid":949945,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"乾冬濕年<br />\n冬唔凍年凍"},{"pid":"2b54927ef27baafba59a693724e042a114d20324","tid":949945,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b5ffdf3798c332923dd9ff4d579aa707e19a2a0","tid":949945,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"乾冬濕年<br />\n冬唔凍年凍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:32:03.000Z","msg":"老人家常說「乾冬濕年」，假如冬至沒有下雨，農曆新年便會下雨。我們翻查天文台記錄，把天文台雨量為零或微量（即少於0.1毫米）的日子定義為乾，雨量為0.1毫米或以上的日子定義為濕。有趣的是，過去十年全屬「乾冬」，而且有七年陽光充沛。至於農曆新年，由於每年的日子並不固定（農曆是陰陽合曆），直接比較意義不大；即使如此，過去十年亦只有四年為「濕年」，因此「乾冬濕年」的準確率只有四成。假如我們把年初二及年初三也計算在內，準確率則有六成。"},{"pid":"2e6aa5456173f9af8b26065f6899b04191cab7f2","tid":949945,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b5ffdf3798c332923dd9ff4d579aa707e19a2a0","tid":949945,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"乾冬濕年<br />\n冬唔凍年凍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:33:35.000Z","msg":"但睇番天文台記錄又好似唔太啱<br />\n<br />\n歷年冬至氣溫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hko.gov.hk/cis/statistic/ext_st_winter_solstice_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fcis%2Fstatistic%2Fext_st_winter_solstice_c.htm&d=fIRXLna9qUL1bxMY6drnYePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=714a5bf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hko.gov.hk/cis/statistic/ext_st_winter_solstice_c.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n歷年立春氣溫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hko.gov.hk/cis/statistic/ext_st_spring_commences_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fcis%2Fstatistic%2Fext_st_spring_commences_c.htm&d=fIRXLna9qUL1bxMY6drnYePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=36cc0a45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hko.gov.hk/cis/statistic/ext_st_spring_commences_c.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8ac1491f3f457de5065e06a4e263f3e7c6eb3659","tid":949945,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:34:01.000Z","msg":"天文台又指，若比較冬至和年初一的最低氣溫，兩者亦沒明顯關係，即「過冬唔凍」不一定「過年凍」。天文台解釋，每年冬至與農曆新年相距的時間並不固定，一般超過一個月，其間影響香港的天氣系統可以有很大變化，所以冬至與農曆新年的天氣狀況，難有特定關係。"},{"pid":"4b2442686406cfe9232848cbc00554cf6f511705","tid":949945,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b54927ef27baafba59a693724e042a114d20324","tid":949945,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b5ffdf3798c332923dd9ff4d579aa707e19a2a0","tid":949945,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"乾冬濕年<br />\n冬唔凍年凍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:32:03.000Z","msg":"老人家常說「乾冬濕年」，假如冬至沒有下雨，農曆新年便會下雨。我們翻查天文台記錄，把天文台雨量為零或微量（即少於0.1毫米）的日子定義為乾，雨量為0.1毫米或以上的日子定義為濕。有趣的是，過去十年全屬「乾冬」，而且有七年陽光充沛。至於農曆新年，由於每年的日子並不固定（農曆是陰陽合曆），直接比較意義不大；即使如此，過去十年亦只有四年為「濕年」，因此「乾冬濕年」的準確率只有四成。假如我們把年初二及年初三也計算在內，準確率則有六成。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:44:28.000Z","msg":"二十四節氣都有一定參考價值，不過二十四節氣始終係北方概念，落到嚟南方大概每個節氣delay兩個禮拜就差唔多"}]}